metadata.name: One eye
metadata.description: ‚ÄèIt was one of the first things I really liked, it was a style I always enjoyed drawing, I heard many times that no, what you are doing is not right, but I continued.  The nude art style is amazing and really the most beautiful thing for me, drawing male and female bodies to make you feel beautiful and nothing else!  Really more beautiful than this beautiful body that our eyes see, I see nothing but the beauty and dancing of the beautiful human body. I wish one day everyone would understand what beautiful things God has created and your eyes can see with all their heart.  I always love eye design because it makes me feel seen, your eyes are the best lens in the whole world, so try to see beauty through it!
